   unstep-◻ (• x 〈 _ 〉∙ _) (• .x 〈 y 〉 ᶜ) = • x 〈 y 〉∙ ◻
   unstep-◻ (E ➕₁ Q) a = [ unstep-◻ E a ] ➕ ◻
   unstep-◻ (E ᵇ│ Q) a = [ unstep-◻ E a ] │ ◻
   unstep-◻ (E ᶜ│ Q) a = [ unstep-◻ E a ] │ ◻
   unstep-◻ (P │ᵇ E) a = ◻ │ [ unstep-◻ E a ]
   unstep-◻ (P │ᶜ E) a = ◻ │ [ unstep-◻ E a ]
